Generate Terraform code for a standard 3-tier AWS architecture with High Availability. The infrastructure should include:

A VPC across 3 Availability Zones with Public and Private subnets.

An Application Load Balancer (ALB) facing the public internet.

An Auto Scaling Group for EC2 instances in the public subnets.

A Multi-AZ RDS database (Primary + Standby) in the private subnets.